May 27, 2019 (PPI-OT)

Four mega CPEC projects launched
body: Prime Minister Imran Khan and Chinese Vice President Wang Qishan Sunday launched four mega development projects in the fields of energy, technology and education under China Pakistan Economic Corridor (CPEC). Both the dignitaries unveiled the plaques of the four projects at a ceremony held here during the visit of the Chinese vice president who is here on three-day visit. https://fp.brecorder.com/2019/05/20190527480932/
